         <p>If you are a US based Fundraisers, you can also choose to use <span>Paypal</span> as your primary payment gateway for all transactions.</p>
         <p>Our payment gateway partner takes a <span>certain</span> fee on every credit or debit card transaction based on plan you select. We do not charge for disbursements.</p>
         <b>We do not charge any commissions or cut from any any donation your receive, neither we ask your donors to pay us a tip. We are truly free to help you make a big difference in this world.</b>
